Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I hate this stupid snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially now that HQ's said we need\Nto be sure to do all our patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up over\NJacott-san, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think there's\Nanything wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can look all you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if you don't find anyone,\Nyou can still believe they're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan, I thought you might be looking\Nlike Rio-sempai for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under that cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four hundred meters or so out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even his clothes are frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, take off his coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll change coats with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Visitor - A Burning Field of Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you were actually able\Nto bring back this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see how you earned your reputation\Nas the greatest genius in academy history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now victory is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you,\NKannagi Noël-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While on patrol, the two\Nof them found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her left leg is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fingers are turning\Nblack and red!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frostbite. If we're not careful,\Nshe'll lose the fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The witch of Helvetia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fingers are OK, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd stay with\Nher for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know... She seemed to think\Nthis was really important,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like when she was fixing\Nthe Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be a spy, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one thought we'd run into\Na Roman soldier there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It was the first time I've ever\Nseen anyone from Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they're all\Nenemies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking they'd\Nbe scarier somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Rome probably\Nthink the same about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I realized, when I saw her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for school\Nlessons to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace talks are still\Ngoing badly, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we reporting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, she'll be taken to the\NCapitol and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're invading enemy territory\Nduring unstable times!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier should be prepared\Nfor torture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will decide what to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me some\Ntime, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you meet anyone when you\Nwere carrying her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Rio. What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Helvetian soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you going\Nto do with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a Helvetian prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't speak Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you took me prisoner-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Roman Army, First Armored\NDivision, 13th Legion B-Company
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant Aisha Aldola,\Nserial number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Roman Army, Warrant Officer\NAisha Aldola, serial number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Identification number 1031021.>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got guts, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't speak any Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:10:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we learned was her serial number\Nand that her name is Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of this fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have really nice breasts,\Njust the kind I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be all right if I played\Nwith them for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I run my fingers\Nall along your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really seems unable to\Nunderstand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a problem. We can't\Ninterrogate her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find someone\Nwho speaks Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can interrogate her\Nand file a proper report,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll keep her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd place a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no part in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-chan, welcome to\NClocktower Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Clocktower Fortress?>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, Clocktower Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Ah, I see... Then I made it.>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Grandmother...>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<To escape, I need stamina,\Nso I'll eat your food.>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's saying it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata's always like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Noël's never that\Nnice to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be trying to atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen\Na fossil of an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<They don't understand me, I know...\NWhat's wrong with me?>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have studied Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could talk, we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yumina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys got enough people at\Nthe church to help shovel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are really working at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they're really growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People grow and get\Nbetter every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Kanata-san's\Ntrumpet playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio would say she's not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, weren't you heading to\NTreize to buy more goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some stuff happened, and I ended up\Nhaving to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speaking of the Fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this awful rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<It's a wonderful melody.>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Ah, I didn't know there were\Ntrumpets like that left.>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Can I play it?>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Rio-sempai would let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<It's a good trumpet.>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Really, I haven't seen\None this nice...>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That song was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya's song filled me up, and then Rio-sempai's,\Nand the same song is in Roman, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound really does fill the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same way in Rome\Nand in Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Danke.>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan...ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Yeah, danke.>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "danke"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought someone saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This city never bore the\Nfull brunt of the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but almost everyone here's lost family and\Nfriends, one way or another, in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nice people,\Nbut you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikhail,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you remember the guy who\Nruns that distillery?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was at his place until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said the Helvetian\NArmy's on the move,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,heading here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's got something to do with a Roman\Nscout being all the way out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san, do you know anyone\Nwho speaks Roman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a servant of the Helvetian\NOrthodox Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May the blessings of\Nthe all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That greeting is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell us, you put everyone\Nhere in a very bad position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel any sort of obligation to them,\Nthen tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you about my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to see the\NAngel Fossil located in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she wants to\Nsee the Angel Fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Fossil...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother was\Na Maiden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother was\Na soldier here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<She was captured at the Eastern Front\Nand met my grandfather.>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was captured at the Eastern Front\Nand met my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<As I grew up, I listened\Nto her stories.>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up listening to her stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<So I wanted to see the Angel of the apocalypse\Nthat brought judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the world in the distant past,\Nthe one my grandmother spoke of.>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doctrine is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the devil that destroyed\Nthe world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us exactly\Nwhat she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see the angel of the apocalypse\Nthat destroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she came...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A call to advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That code is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Royal Guard Platoon, 9th Independent\NMobile Division...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 9th... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Hopkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's known as the\NDemon of Vingt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he brought weapons\Nback from the old age,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wiping out three towns\Nin a single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. He doesn't\Nknow you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you don't have\Ntime to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to decide what you're\Ngoing to do, and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can either give her over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Helvetian Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't make it in\Ntime, did you, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio didn't want anyone\Nelse to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she'd do what\Nshe could, she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she left, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now give my order as leader\Nof the 1121st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This order is mine alone, and I will\Ntake full responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we clear, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Commander of the 1121st Platoon,\NLieutenant Filicia Heidemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, a Roman scout\Nwas captured in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there was an accident during\Nquestioning, and we didn't get any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've actually had reports of\Na Roman soldier here in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment,\Nthe 1121st Fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is under the command of the 9th\NIndependent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha was telling me about the\Nlegend of the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gotta be here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Post more guards by the exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't asked your name\Nyet, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ihr name ist Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël... Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Witch of Helvetia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Reaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rat, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:21:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 1121st Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A massive Roman Army contingent has appeared\Nat the Seize border with No Man's Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fill the Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.07,0:24:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill the Blue Sky.
